Class AbstractRestServiceTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.assertj.core.api.Assertions

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TablemanagementRestServiceTest

    @SpringApplicationConfiguration(classes=RestaurantTestConfig.class)
@WebIntegrationTest
@ActiveProfiles(profiles="junit")
public abstract class AbstractRestServiceTest
extends io.oasp.module.test.common.base.SubsystemTest
    Abstract base class for SubsystemTests which runs the tests within a local server.

    The local server's port is randomly assigned.
    Author:
    jmolinar
